@startuml sequence-happy
title Добавление расхода (Happy Path)
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Член семьи" as User
participant "WebApp UI" as UI
participant "Budget API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Push Service" as Push

User -> UI: Ввод суммы, категории, описания
activate UI

UI -> API: POST /api/expenses\n(amount, category_id, user_id)
activate API

API -> DB: SELECT limit, spent FROM categories WHERE id = category_id
activate DB
DB --> API: limit_ok (Лимит не превышен)
deactivate DB

API -> DB: INSERT INTO expenses (amount, ...)
activate DB
DB --> API: OK, expense_id
deactivate DB

API -> API: Обновление кэша баланса

API -> Push: Отправить уведомление семье (асинхронно)
activate Push
Push --> API: Очередь принята
deactivate Push

API --> UI: 201 Created
deactivate API

UI --> User: "Расход успешно добавлен"
deactivate UI
@enduml